::Prowl::

"No Khonokolor, we are going to help the Chivtron's. Now come on."
Prowl looked around. Himself, Hot Rod, Skyburst, Epyon, Khonkolor, and
the Xenoforce. That made 10. A good fighting force. He turns to Ghost
and Goth, still waiting for them to say yes or no.
"Well guys, you in or not?"
